{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_016kwHSRmL8tDkhotvX1GSCL","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the problems:\n\n1. On `/app`:\n   - `app-user` has empty configure permission (no configure) - needs `.*`\n   - `ops-user` has full permissions on `/app` - needs to be removed\n   \n2. On `/ops`:\n   - `ops-user` has NO permissions at all - needs `.*` `.*` `.*`\n   - `app-user` doesn't appear on `/ops` (good, it has no permissions there)\n\nRequired end state:\n- `app-user`: full `.*` `.*` `.*` on `/app`, NO permissions on `/ops`\n- `ops-user`: full `.*` `.*` `.*` on `/ops`, NO permissions on `/app`\n\nI need to run three commands: grant `app-user` full permissions on `/app`, remove `ops-user` from `/app`, and grant `ops-user` full permissions on `/ops`.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":434,"cache_read_input_tokens":29378,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":434},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"05dd6e4a-50d4-4cbf-819d-1b2ec0230a78","uuid":"e3d04834-a346-442f-a960-58b18ecd27df","request_id":"req_011CcbvqjvWwjUoYVmwdRZAT"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_016kwHSRmL8tDkhotvX1GSCL","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The issues are clear:\n- `/app`: `app-user` has empty configure (`\"\"`), `ops-user` has full access (shouldn't)\n- `/ops`: `ops-user` has no permissions at all\n\nFixing all three issues now:"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":434,"cache_read_input_tokens":29378,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":434},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"05dd6e4a-50d4-4cbf-819d-1b2ec0230a78","uuid":"43339442-18f2-413f-9681-bc5aab78a5f1","request_id":"req_011CcbvqjvWwjUoYVmwdRZAT"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_016kwHSRmL8tDkhotvX1GSCL","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01EoX4x4Zvf9EsMNPBmWpLF9","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"NS=\"karma-rabbitmq-full-lifecycle-04-2026-2293b2c1-cluster-a\"\n\n# Fix app-user configure on /app (was empty string)\nkubectl -n $NS exec rabbitmq-0 -- rabbitmqctl set_permissions -p /app app-user \".*\" \".*\" \".*\"\n\n# Remove ops-user from /app (wrong vhost)\nkubectl -n $NS exec rabbitmq-0 -- rabbitmqctl clear_permissions -p /app ops-user\n\n# Grant ops-user full permissions on /ops (was missing entirely)\nkubectl -n $NS exec rabbitmq-0 -- rabbitmqctl set_permissions -p /ops ops-user \".*\" \".*\" \".*\"","description":"Fix RabbitMQ permissions"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":434,"cache_read_input_tokens":29378,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":434},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"05dd6e4a-50d4-4cbf-819d-1b2ec0230a78","uuid":"672cf29f-c761-4cfc-9e01-f858a2a1565b","request_id":"req_011CcbvqjvWwjUoYVmwdRZAT"}
